v><div class="item-body"><p class="description">知乎发起的在线嘉宾讨论，详情请点击：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/question/20886632" data-editable="true" data-title="什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与" class="">什么是「知乎圆桌」？如何参与</a>？<br>圆桌页面：<a href="http://www.zhihu.com/roundtable" data-editable="true" data-title="活动">活动列表</a></p></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/topic/20190187" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='t$t$20190187'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-e8ebe745a77093efc081d4bc1fea599f_l.jpg" alt=" 京师心理大学堂" class="avatar d50"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/topic/20190187" class="name" data-hovercard='t$t$20190187'> 京师心理大学堂</a><div class="bio">举办过 1 场圆桌</div></div></div><div class="item-body"><p class="description">京师心理大学堂，由北京师范大学心理学部出品，立志做最优质的心理科普，让这里成为当代人们追求幸福美满生活的大学堂。奉献百年积淀，带你脑洞大开。</p></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module guests"><div class="module-header"><h3>嘉宾</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items"><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/yuan-xin-83-10" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$yuan-xin-83-10'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-17df4014491558eaddf7b10917b9c1cb_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="Circle Yuan"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/qiaoshengyiyu/yuan-xin-83-10/answers" class="answers text-muted">2 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/yuan-xin-83-10" data-hovercard='p$t$yuan-xin-83-10'>Circle Yuan</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">朋克（Punk Rock）</div></div></div></li><li class="item"><div class="item-header"><a href="/people/chen-zhuo-49" class="item-link" tabindex="-1" data-hovercard='p$t$chen-zhuo-49'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-afcb8fcc1795e2910718032ab3245fe7_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="陈茁"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/qiaoshengyiyu/chen-zhuo-49/answers" class="answers text-muted">1 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/che